channel.title: Dungeoneering Tab [Pi]
channel.description:
Hey guys im currently working on a dungeoneering project on a 317 pi and im going to rip it after im finished and put it on my server extremex-scape. So heres some pics and progress notes. Suggestions are welcome. Feel free to suggest different floors the floors that i have atm aren't guarented floors so if you think you know a better one just tell me the coords and ill check it out, also feel free to suggest different colors on the dungeoneering tab.
[b]Alot of the floors have different settings because i dont want them all to be in one area and it makes them look unique.[/b]
Progress log: [code]All floors named in the tab 100 % All floors tele to correct location 100% All portals are spawned 100% You can't tele there over 20 wildy 100 % You can't tele there in jail 100% Dung leveling 10 % Npc warning dudes 100%(What they are, is i made a couple invisbile barriers and they yell outloud on a couple of the floors every so often "You can't pass here!" Boss spawns 100 % Portal Teleporting 100 % Dung keys 100 % Dung exchange 100 % Dung Tokens 100 % [/code]
